### REST Client for CSE341 Contacts API
### Use this file to test all API endpoints

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@apiUrl = http://localhost:3000/api/contacts

### ============================================
### GET ALL CONTACTS
### ============================================
GET {{apiUrl}} HTTP/1.1


### ============================================
### CREATE A NEW CONTACT
### ============================================
POST {{apiUrl}} HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "favoriteColor": "Blue",
  "birthday": "1990-01-15T00:00:00.000Z"
}

